---
title: BBQ Chicken Burger with aioli and spiced chips
description: A USA-inspired feast, this chicken burger calls on key flavours of the American South. BBQ rub coats the golden chips (or as they call them stateside—french fries) while a finger-licking BBQ sauce marinates the juicy chicken steaks.
